name: UnmodifiableSortedSet_unmodifiableSortedSetTest
description: Unit tests for the UnmodifiableSortedSet class, focusing on the unmodifiableSortedSet method.

test_cases.name: testUnmodifiableSortedSetWithUnmodifiableSet
test_cases.description: Tests that wrapping an unmodifiable set with UnmodifiableSortedSet.unmodifiableSortedSet returns the same instance.

test_cases.name: testUnmodifiableSortedSetWithModifiableSet
test_cases.description: Tests that wrapping a modifiable set with UnmodifiableSortedSet.unmodifiableSortedSet returns an unmodifiable instance.

test_cases.name: testUnmodifiableSortedSetWithNullSet
test_cases.description: Tests that passing null to UnmodifiableSortedSet.unmodifiableSortedSet throws a NullPointerException.
